init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Soeurette kidnaps Matt Damon for his immense talent of playing the ukulele.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And so the game begins, Matt Damon must escape from planet Doozy by playing the ukulele and over a period of years, becomes an

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The game is called Ukulele Hero.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is here that Matt Damon must face his greatest challenge.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon must master such exotic ukulele songs as "The Entertainer", "Smoke on the Water", and "This Land Is

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon must play a song every couple of minutes or Soeurette will start to get angry.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon is very anxious to escape from planet Doozy as he has had enough of being a slave to Soeurette.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon has almost reached the end of his ukulele playing days and is very close to freedom.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The only thing that stands in his way is the hardest song he has ever played on planet Doozy; "The Way We Were."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon is ready for his moment to shine.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The time has come for Matt Damon to face Soeurette and play her his finest ukulele performance.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This ceremony will be ultimate for Matt Damon and his ukulele playing abilities.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon walks out in front of the crowds and plays his heart out.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He plays the chords perfectly and nails his rhythm.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The crowd looks on in utter amazement at Matt Damon's ukulele playing abilities.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He finishes the song and the crowd erupts in applause.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon looks at Soeurette, trying to read her mind.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Does he get his freedom now?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Soeurette smiles at Matt Damon, signifying that she is impressed with his performance.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon's heart beats faster with excitement.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He looks at Soeurette and she says "That was very good, now go make me a sandwich!"
